style":{"fontSize":"1.1875rem","lineHeight":"1.65"},"children":"Hi, I'm Adrián. It's a pleasure to meet you."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-prose space-y-6 text-base text-ink","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":["I'm ",["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold","children":"Adrián Álvarez"}],". I study finance and technology at the VU Amsterdam and University of Amsterdam, as part of a joint honours programme between the two universities. I'm originally from Spain, and moving abroad has shaped how I see things — being surrounded by people from different countries and disciplines has made me more comfortable with ambiguity and more curious about why systems behave the way they do."]}],"$Lb","$Lc","$Ld","$Le"]}],"$Lf","$L10"]}]}],["$L11"],"$L12"]}],{},null,false]},null,false]},null,false],"$L13",false]],"m":"$undefined","G":["$14",["$L15"]],"s":false,"S":true}
